snippet.title: Raft - The Final Chapter Trailer
snippet.description:
Hello Rafters! We are happy to announce that The Final Chapter is releasing on June 20! It’s by far our biggest update yet! New destinations, new playable characters, new enemies, more story and many new exciting features. 

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/648800/Raft/

Don't forget to follow us on our social media as well! 

Discord: https://discord.gg/raft
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RaftSurvivaGame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/RaftGame 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/redbeetinteractive/?hl=sv
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/RaftTheGame
